  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: adresses https://github.com/react-native-community/react-native-camera/issues/1234 and logged for tracking purposes\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nuser is able to use camera:\r\n- to scan QRs\r\n- to make a user picture\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nblack screen shown when using camera on Android\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Tap Profile -> Edit ->Capture\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n<RNCamera\r\nref={(cam) => { this.camera = cam; }}\r\ntype={RNCamera.Constants.Type.back}\r\n// onBarCodeRead={this.barcodeRead}\r\nbarCodeTypes={[RNCamera.Constants.BarCodeType.qr]}\r\nstyle={styles.preview}\r\n>\r\n<Text style={styles.capture} onPress={this.emulateScan}>[id: 4 code: 5K0C3H]</Text>\r\n<TouchableOpacity onPress={() => Alert.alert('Alert', 'Keyboard pressed')}>\r\n<Image source={imgKeyboard} style={[styles.icon]} />\r\n</TouchableOpacity>\r\n</RNCamera>\r\n\r\n",
